metadata.name: Andy Warhol. A minute before the fatal shot
metadata.description: The incredible collection of the artist Feniks Flamm "The non-fungible Andy Warhol" reveals the full potential of Andy Warhol's works in the world of NFT. The collection is based on the works of Feniks "The Genius Andy Warhol" and "Andy Warhol. A minute before the fatal shot." The main idea of the collection is to immerse the viewer in the atmosphere of the legendary Warhol factory and answer the question: what could be the works of the cult master of pop art in the era of cryptocurrencies and NFT.
